params._base: The base to convert the number to
params._number: The unsigned integer to be converted to a string
params._padding: The target length of the string; result will be padded with 0 to reach this length while padding         of 0 means no padding

returns._0: bytes The resulting ASCII string value

toString(uint256,uint8,uint8).notice: To String Converts an unsigned integer to the string equivalent value, returned as bytes Equivalent to javascript's toString(base)
